description: This file provides an implementation of a platform-dependent utility function to create a CWMP session object within the CCSP framework. It primarily exposes the function CcspCwmpCreateWmpSession which internally calls CcspCwmpsoCreate, and includes license and module information.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE CcspCwmpCreateWmpSession(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a new CCSP CWMP session object by calling an internal creation function, passing through context handles.
